# 灯光

## 灯光的结构

![](data:image/webp;base64,)
[[Directional Lights.pdf#page=11&rect=24,298,574,511&color=note|Directional Lights, p.11]]
对于平行光，我们只考虑关的方向和颜色。

## 光照函数

```HLSL
// （根据法线和入射光的夹角）获取表面进光  
float3 IncomingLight(Surface surface, Light light)  
{  
    return saturate(dot(surface.normal, light.direction)) * light.color;  
}  
  
// 获取表面反照光  
float3 GetLighting(Surface surface, Light light)  
{  
    return IncomingLight(surface, light) * surface.color;  
}  
  
float3 GetLighting(Surface surface)  
{  
    return GetLighting(surface, GetDirectionalLight());  
}
```

## 发送光照数据到GPU

到目前为止，都是使用的自己创建的光照数据，应该需要使用到Unity场景中提供的灯光数据。

在`CBUFFER_START`块中，定义灯光数据，这样着色器才能正确获取灯光数据：
```HLSL
CBUFFER_START(CustomLit)  
    float3 _DirectionalLightColor;  
    float3 _DirectionalLightDirection;  
CBUFFER_END
```

![](data:image/webp;base64,)
[[Directional Lights.pdf#page=14&rect=23,52,581,331&color=note|Directional Lights, p.14]]
创建一个`Lighting`类，用于将自定义的灯光数据发送给GPU。

使用`RenderSettings.sun`获取到场景主光源，然后将颜色和方向赋值给我们自定义的灯光数据：
```CSharp
private void SetupDirectionalLight()  
{  
    Light light = RenderSettings.sun;  
    this._buffer.SetGlobalVector(dirLightColorId, 
							    light.color.linear * light.intensity);  
    this._buffer.SetGlobalVector(dirLightDirectionId, -
							    light.transform.forward);  
}
```

>[!QUESTION]
> 为什么这里传递给Shader的灯光方向取了负值？

## 可见光

实际上来说，Unity在剔除阶段就会计算出哪些光照会影响到摄像机的可视空间，然后将其存放在`visibleLights`属性中（这是一个NativeArray数组），因此可以使用这些数据，而非场景主光源。

## 多个平行光

```CSharp
private const int MaxDirLightCounts = 4;  
private static int  
    dirLightCountId = Shader.PropertyToID("_DirectionalLightCount"),  
    dirLightColorsId = Shader.PropertyToID("_DirectionalLightColors"),  
    dirLightDirectionsId = Shader.PropertyToID("_DirectionalLightDirections");  
private static Vector4[]  
    dirLightColors = new Vector4[MaxDirLightCounts],  
    dirLightDirections = new Vector4[MaxDirLightCounts];
```
使用以上的数组结构，将多个灯光数据发送给GPU。
> [!PDF|yellow] [[Directional Lights.pdf#page=18&selection=101,0,113,7&color=yellow|Directional Lights, p.18]]
> > Why not use structured buffers? That's possible, but I won't because shader support for structured buffers isn't good enough yet. Either they're not supported at all, are only in fragment programs, or perform worse than regular arrays. The good news is that the specifics of how data is passed between CPU and GPU only matter in a few places, so it's is easy to change. That's another benefit of using the Light struct.
> 
> `Structured Buffers`支持不好，并且性能不行

```CSharp
private void SetupDirectionalLight(int index, VisibleLight visibleLight)  
{  
    dirLightColors[index] = visibleLight.finalColor;  
    dirLightDirections[index] = -visibleLight.localToWorldMatrix.GetColumn(2); 
}
```
使用`finalColor`可以直接获取计算了光强的光的颜色。从`localToWorldMatrix`矩阵中，可以获取光的方向。

由于传递给着色器的灯光数据是数组，因此，着色器的灯光数据也需要同步修改一下。
